{"data":[{"date":"16:44 21/08","title":"Morata \u0111\u1eb7t ra m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/morata-dat-ra-muc-tieu-lon-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi m\u1edf t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMorata \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Chelsea<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge, sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn t\u1eeb BL\u0110 v\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Alvaro Morata c\u0169ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Arsenal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 ni\u1ec1m tin. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd tr\u00f4i qua ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u00f4i t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ghi tr\u00ean 30 b\u00e0n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn, t\u00f4i th\u00edch ghi 15-20 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League h\u01a1n, ho\u1eb7c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/morata-toi-chua-tung-nghi-den-chuyen-roi-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt trong v\u00f2ng 1 th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111ang \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c theo h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 CLB n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal. T\u1ea1i Premier League, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu-172-194971.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu-172-194971.html\">Eden Hazard s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Chelsea n\u1ebfu...</span><br>\r\nEden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2019 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd The Sun \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chi-ra-ly-do-khien-arsenal-that-bai-truoc-chelsea-172-194932.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/huyen-thoai-chi-ra-ly-do-khien-arsenal-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chi-ra-ly-do-khien-arsenal-that-bai-truoc-chelsea-172-194932.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</span><br>\r\nIan Wright ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Alexandre Lacazette l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2615","checkdouble":"194991"},{"date":"16:32 21/08","title":"Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bahrain. V\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ecb d\u01a1 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain b\u1edfi \u1edf 4 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 3. V\u00e0 h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<h2>1. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U19 Bahrain (2016)</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U19 Bahrain t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 n\u0103m 2016.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Bahrain nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Tr\u1ea7n Th\u00e0nh.\u00a0Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2017 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1edfi \u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 11 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Olympic Bahrain \u0111ang c\u00f3 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng thua U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m. V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eefa tr\u01b0\u1edbc Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u1edf l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn gi\u1eefa b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn gi\u1eefa b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bahrain \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-1 Olympic Bahrain (2010)</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ASIAD 2010, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. \u1ede b\u1ea3ng B c\u00f9ng Olympic Iran, Turkmenistan v\u00e0 Bahrain, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1 chung cu\u1ed9c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0110inh Thanh Trung l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ph\u00fat 34 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ghi th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam 2010\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2010\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/viet-nam-bahrain-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u0103m 2010 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 Bahrain t\u1ea1i ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Bahrain sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 do Isa ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ASIAD n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-1 Olympic Bahrain c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD b\u1edfi nh\u1edd 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<h2>3. \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam 5-3 Bahrain (2007)</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m VCK Asian Cup 2007, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Bahrain \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110TQG. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1edfng, v\u00f4 ph\u1ea1t, hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 c\u1edfi m\u1edf v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho NHM.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Abdulrahman l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 sau sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n D\u01b0\u01a1ng H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n Nhi\u00ean, C\u00f4ng Vinh v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn Th\u00e0nh l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 11, 16 v\u00e0 52 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i 3-1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, s\u1ef1 l\u01a1 l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00fap Bahrain c\u00f3 hai b\u00e0n g\u1ee1, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Thanh B\u00ecnh v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 5-3.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u00e2n h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c xem th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0110T Malaysia c\u1ee7a BHL \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chinh-thuc-da-co-ban-quyen-asiad-tai-viet-nam-168-194974.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/chinh-thuc-da-co-ban-quyen-asiad-tai-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chinh-thuc-da-co-ban-quyen-asiad-tai-viet-nam-168-194974.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 l\u00e3nh th\u1ed5 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\">HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2614","checkdouble":"194992"},{"date":"17:18 21/08","title":"Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua sao tr\u1ebb Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/8/barca-chot-gia-mua-adrien-rabiot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, t\u1edd Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ramsey t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 2 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 Arsenal c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Emery, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Emery, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/ramsey-choang-vang-voi-quyet-dinh-cua-hlv-unai-emery.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramsey kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Chelsea HLV Unai Emery s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Guendouzi v\u00e0 Xhaka \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, Mesut Ozil ch\u01a1i trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 10. Aaron Ramsey b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 67 thay Ozil.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, t\u1edd Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRamsey kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Wenger c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, b\u1edfi v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb HLV Emery lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch khi\u1ebfn anh r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal t\u0103ng l\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, Ramsey \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Unai Emery. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111ang l\u00ean l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aaron Ramsey\" title=\"Aaron Ramsey\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-aaron-ramsey.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aaron Ramsey ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Ramsey v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Emery tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n khi\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ramsey t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 ra \u0111i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-ramsey-va-vecino-172-192315.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng mua Ramsey</span> v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2018, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Sanchez t\u1edbi M.U, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ramsey r\u1eddi Emirates v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2613","checkdouble":"194994"},{"date":"17:45 21/08","title":"B\u1ea1n c\u0169 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/jason-denayer-sap-roi-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng \u0103n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn t\u1eeb CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Denayer kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf Man City</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJason Denayer t\u1eebng c\u00f3 5 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u1edf l\u00f2 JMG n\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng t\u1edbi trung t\u00e2m Trung t\u00e2m th\u1ec3 thao H\u00e0m R\u1ed3ng (Gia Lai) \u0103n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb HAGL bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd tay b\u1eaft m\u1eb7t m\u1eebng, \u0111\u1ed5i \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu gi\u1eefa Man City v\u00e0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2015.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m 2013, Denayer chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Man City. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb CLB v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Celtic, Galatasaray hay Sunderland. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh to\u00e0n sao c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/jason-denayer-sap-roi-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Lyon</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDenayer kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Man City v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn \u01b0a th\u00edch l\u00e0 Lyon c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ban \u0111\u1ea7u The Citizens kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t anh. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y sang ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u201canh em\u201d c\u00f9ng t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n City Football Group l\u00e0 Girona d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Lyon. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro (9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) v\u00e0 r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh t\u1eeb Man City. Th\u00f4ng qua Twitter, Man City c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y: \u201cCh\u00fac may m\u1eafn, Jason Denayer, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Lyon.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng bao g\u1ed3m ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, Denayer s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Lyon. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u201cS\u01b0 t\u1eed s\u00f4ng Rhone\u201d c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch Ligue 1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 ch\u1ec9 sau Paris Saint-Germain v\u00e0 Monaco.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-john-stones-172-194898.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-ruben-neves-vao-thang-1-172-194884.html\">Man City chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ruben Neves v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/patrick-roberts-sap-roi-man-city-sang-girona-172-194473.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t sao tr\u1ebb chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sterling-toa-sang-tro-lai-guardiola-cau-khan-gia-han-voi-man-city-172-194465.html\">Sterling t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Guardiola c\u1ea7u kh\u1ea9n gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-co-vai-dieu-muon-gui-den-man-city-va-sterling-172-194403.html\">Pep c\u00f3 v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Man City v\u00e0 Sterling</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-man-city-het-tien-mua-cau-thu-roi-172-194212.html\">Pep Guardiola: \u201cMan City h\u1ebft ti\u1ec1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i!\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2612","checkdouble":"194995"},{"date":"17:13 21/08","title":"MU ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ra sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/mu-phan-ung-ra-sao-sau-tin-don-sa-thai-mourinho-bo-nhiem-zidane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd BBC c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1eafm Zidane thay Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/MU-sa-thai-Jose-Mourinho-bo-nhiem-Zinedine-Zidane--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1eafm Zidane thay Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng M.U v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u00e0o Top 4 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng M.U sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, M.U nh\u1eafm Zinedine Zidane trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 Zidane n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd BBC c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ra sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"MU ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ra sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/mu-phan-ung-ra-sao-sau-tin-don-sa-thai-mourinho-bo-nhiem-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb M.U n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd BBC: \u201cT\u1ea1i sao ch\u00fang ta l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn Zidane khi Mourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Zidane thay Mourinho. BL\u0110 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Mourinho\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin gi\u1eefa Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 M.U \u0111ang xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-va-bld-mu-mau-thuan-vi-anthony-martial-172-194990.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 M.U c\u0169ng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1ec1 Martial</span>. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial ngay \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2611","checkdouble":"194996"},{"date":"17:30 21/08","title":"Ramsey cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Unai Emery","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/ramsey-choang-vang-voi-quyet-dinh-cua-hlv-unai-emery.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, t\u1edd Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ramsey t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 2 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 Arsenal c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Emery, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Emery, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/ramsey-choang-vang-voi-quyet-dinh-cua-hlv-unai-emery.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramsey kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Chelsea HLV Unai Emery s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 v\u1edbi Guendouzi v\u00e0 Xhaka \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, Mesut Ozil ch\u01a1i trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 10. Aaron Ramsey b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 67 thay Ozil.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, t\u1edd Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRamsey kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n h\u00e0ng tu\u1ea7n. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Wenger c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, b\u1edfi v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb HLV Emery lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch khi\u1ebfn anh r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal t\u0103ng l\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, Ramsey \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Unai Emery. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111ang l\u00ean l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aaron Ramsey\" title=\"Aaron Ramsey\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-aaron-ramsey.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Aaron Ramsey ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Ramsey v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Emery tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n khi\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ramsey t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u00e0 ra \u0111i l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-ramsey-va-vecino-172-192315.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng mua Ramsey</span> v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2018, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Sanchez t\u1edbi M.U, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ramsey r\u1eddi Emirates v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2610","checkdouble":"194997"},{"date":"17:09 21/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf ASIAD?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u00f9a v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u1eeba qua, trong khi L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 suy ngh\u0129 kh\u00e1c.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qatar v\u00e0 Bangladesh, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Worrawoot Srimaka ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng B v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 24 n\u0103m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out ASIAD. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Bao-chi-Thai-Lan-chi-trich-doi-nha-sau-that-bai-o-Asiad-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd Siamsport gi\u1eadt d\u00f2ng t\u00edt th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn: \u201c\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nam Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb nghi\u1ec1n n\u00e1t\u201d. T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp trung ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch hai y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 do L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT) v\u00e0 HLV Worrawoot Srimaka.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Siamsport cho r\u1eb1ng FAT \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV Srimaka l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Siamsport, t\u1edd Bangkok Post cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i U23 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan Somyot Poompunmuang \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c HLV Worrawoot Srimaka. \u201cL\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3m t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ed7i khi m\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eb3ng HLV n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng sa th\u1ea3i HLV Worrawoot. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean logic. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng C\u0110V Th\u00e1i Lan c\u0169ng n\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn logic\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bahrain. V\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u00e2n h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c xem th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0110T Malaysia c\u1ee7a BHL \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/vff5479-15341729950901227889727.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2609","checkdouble":"195000"},{"date":"17:10 21/08","title":"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Palace 0-2 Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-palace-02-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng gi\u00f2n gi\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i Man City \u1edf top \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho Liverpool\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Palace 0-2 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Liverpool mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i, thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 huy. Nh\u01b0ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u00f3 Van Dijk v\u00e0 Alisson, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a The Kop \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace, HLV Jurgen Klopp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Alexander-Arnold, Joe Gomez, Van Dijk v\u00e0 Andy Robertson. Ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Benteke, Townsend v\u00e0 Zaha nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Liverpool v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVan Dijk g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng. Anh th\u1eafng 8/11 l\u1ea7n tranh ch\u1ea5p tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng. Joe Gomez c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha c\u1eaft b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng quan tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRobertson v\u00e0 Alexander-Arnold c\u0169ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00e2ng cao v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Palace kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m d\u00e2ng cao. \u1ede trong khung g\u1ed7, Alisson t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 huy c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<h2>Alisson ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Alisson gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Van Dijk, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ed1t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Liverpool ngay khi v\u1eeba c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd r\u1ea5t v\u1eefng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 huy h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlisson b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1eed th\u00e1ch \u1edf ph\u00fat 54 khi Milivojevic \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, Benteke c\u0169ng tung ra m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh khi\u1ebfn Alisson ph\u1ea3i d\u01b0\u1edbn ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee9u thua. Anh c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn ra ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eeb xa. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ee3i d\u00e2y li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a The Kop.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Liverpool k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n Palace c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t 21 trong 23 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 11 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00f2n tr\u1ecba c\u1ee7a Alisson. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea1i sao anh l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<h2>Mane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mane\" title=\"Mane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/170848-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mane \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Wan-Bissaka c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u00ea b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. Nh\u01b0ng Sadio Mane m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean r\u00ea b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi 5/6 l\u1ea7n \u0111i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, sau khi ghi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi West Ham tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Salah thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u00e0 Firmino d\u1ea1t qu\u00e1 r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, Mane ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u1edbi Man City.</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp\" title=\"Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Klopp c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chinh chi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh tay, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Alisson. Chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0 Shaqiri hay Fabinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Klopp \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 v\u0169 kh\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh Man City t\u1ea1i Premier League cho \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Champions League sau khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t k\u1ef3 t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Liverpool th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Klopp. Sau khi h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t West Ham h\u1ed3i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2608","checkdouble":"195001"},{"date":"17:44 21/08","title":"B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1edd Chosun (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p Bahrain, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng E t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, t\u1edd Chosun (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Bahrain-Khi-ASIAD-bay-gio-moi-thuc-s-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u00e1o Chosun H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, s\u1ef1 tr\u1ed7i d\u1eady c\u1ee7a Bahrain c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Bahrain c\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1edbi 0-6 nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Malaysia 3-2. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c cao \u0111\u1ed9 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain\", t\u1edd Chosun vi\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Song tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Bahrain c\u00f2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Iran. Ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eabn c\u00f2n d\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Chosun, t\u1edd b\u00e1o Hankooki c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Bahrain, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. N\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u Palestine \u2013 Syria\".\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bahrain. V\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad-168-195000.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad-168-195000.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf ASIAD?</span><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u00f9a v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u1eeba qua, trong khi L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 suy...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u00e2n h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c xem th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0110T Malaysia c\u1ee7a BHL \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2607","checkdouble":"195003"},{"date":"17:48 21/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 21/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2108.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 21/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec Bale, Real t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2108 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2108 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2108-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale khi\u1ebfn Real t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGareth Bale \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Lopetegui t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong 2 tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh-180-194897.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/real-madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh-180-194897.html\">Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong 2 tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Edinson Cavani\" title=\"tien dao Edinson Cavani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/18/Real-Madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 mua Edinson Cavani</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani, theo Diario Gol \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chia tay Chelsea trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Neymar s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yuri Berchiche, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf Paris Saint-Germain, tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng xa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ebfp Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Luka Modric ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Emilio Butragueno c\u1ee7a Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Modric \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ecdi tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm Falcao n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Real Madrid \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 30 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Falcao c\u1ee7a Monaco, Los Blancos \u0111ang c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Karim Benzema \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Werner g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Leipzig</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Leipzig, Timo Werner s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Leipzig.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Robert Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Bayern Munich tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Robert Lewandowski \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Valencia ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Rodrigo v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 107 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Valencia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rodrigo cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 107 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2606","checkdouble":"195004"},{"date":"09:27 21/08","title":"Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial trong 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-yeu-cau-mu-ban-martial-trong-1-tuan-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Ed Woodward b\u00e1n sao tr\u1ebb Martial tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda.</h2><h2>Martial ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial trong 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial trong 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/mourinho-yeu-cau-mu-ban-martial-trong-1-tuan-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Anthony Martial g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau khi g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu cho Mourinho. Anh r\u1eddi tour du \u0111\u1ea5u M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a MU t\u1eeb s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 hai ra \u0111\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i l\u00e0 Martial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 Carrington b\u00e1o danh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi Martial kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edbm h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/martial-bi-phat-nang-vi-bo-tap-chong-doi-mourinho-172-192498.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u00f3 \u00fap m\u1edf vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea1t Martial 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton khi Alexis Sanchez b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng Martial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc The Seagulls v\u00e0 b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n sau 1 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brighton k\u1ebft th\u00fac, t\u1edd Daily Star \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u bu\u1ed9c gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Martial.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Martial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n chi ti\u00eau trong th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, HLV Sam Allardyce \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng Martial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMartial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cho Man United. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u01b0ng Man United \u0111\u00e3 mua nh\u1ea7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ea5t r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 bao. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Leroy Sane. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/victor-lindelof-bat-ngo-tho-lo-uoc-mo-khong-the-tin-duoc-172-194938.html\">Victor Lindelof b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-can-co-trach-nhiem-voi-ke-hoach-mua-sam-cua-minh-172-194925.html\">Mourinho c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2605","checkdouble":"194957"},{"date":"09:29 21/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Ipswich 01h45 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nhan-dinh-derby-county-vs-ipswich-01h45-ngay-228-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Derby County vs Ipswich 01h45 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (V\u00f2ng 4 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Ipswich 01h45 ng\u00e0y 228 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Ipswich 01h45 ng\u00e0y 228 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Derby-County-vs-Ipswich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Derby County vs Ipswich</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Derby County vs Ipswich: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea, Frank Lampard tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n gi\u00fap Derby County n\u00e2ng cao v\u1ecb th\u1ebf trong m\u1eaft d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pride Park Derby County \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Ipswich c\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. Song, theo gi\u1edbi ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, Derby County kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng tin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Lampard th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a ch\u01b0a thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. Sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 1-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1, Derby County \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf 2 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leeds ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i, The Ram ch\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi, nh\u1eadn trung b\u00ecnh 2,33 b\u00e0n thua/tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2006/07, Derby County kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft th\u1eafng Ipswich t\u1ea1i Pride Park, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i n\u1ebfm m\u00f9i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 58 tr\u1eadn, Derby County th\u1eafng 21, h\u00f2a 12, thua 25.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Derby County, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 9, h\u00f2a 9, thua 11. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nDerby County: Chris Martin, Ikechi Anya, Curtis Davies (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).<br>\r\nIpswich: Tayo Edun (treo gi\u00f2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2604","checkdouble":"194959"},{"date":"09:37 21/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e0i Ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV s\u1eafp tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 r\u1ebb.</h2><h2>VOV s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Zing, T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c VOV, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf K\u1ef7 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018. VOV v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n xong v\u1edbi KJSM World Corp v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ch\u1ed1t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/lo-dien-don-vi-nam-ban-quyen-phat-song-asiad-2018-tai-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>VOV s\u1eafp tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh\u00a0\u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u00e1c cho bi\u1ebft m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 VOV chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 1.7 tri\u1ec7u USD (x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 39.5 t\u1ec9 VN\u0110). M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 r\u1ebb so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 4 tri\u1ec7u USD m\u00e0 VTV cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a ra khi\u1ebfn hai b\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ASIAD 2018 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u00f4ng tin VOV \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, c\u00e1c m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Vi\u1ec7t Nam tranh t\u00e0i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfu r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>K\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0o \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qua c\u00e1c k\u00eanh chi\u1ebfu \"l\u1eadu\". \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thu h\u00fat nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m h\u01a1n c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \"chui\" l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i. Ph\u00eda VTV \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i r\u1eb1ng v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ra gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i xem \"chui\" l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, vi\u1ec7c xem qua c\u00e1c k\u00eanh kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn NHM m\u1ea5t h\u1ee9ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu VOV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu ASIAD 2018 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung-168-194960.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\">\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf b\u1ea3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\">HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-218-cua-doan-ttvn-472-194942.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/8 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi-168-194910.html\">B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2603","checkdouble":"194960"},{"date":"10:15 21/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/vff5479-15341729950901227889727.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan, Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua. Ngo\u00e0i y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u0103ng hoa.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/vff5479-15341729950901227889727.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Park Hang Seo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb: \u201cC\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u. T\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng m\u1edf l\u00f2ng v\u00e0 th\u1eadt th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i b\u1edfi s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i th\u00ec s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec. D\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac t\u00f4i h\u01a1i lo l\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ko \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n Vi\u1ec7t Nam, s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e3 l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i hay th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp trung, nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n \u1edf ASIAD 18.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n c\u00e1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u00f4ng Park c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 19 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 thay ph\u1ea7n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 g\u1eb7p Bahrain. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c l\u1eabn kinh nghi\u1ec7m, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung-168-194960.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung-168-194960.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\">\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf b\u1ea3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 trong m\u01a1 m\u1edbi x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1edbi \u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\">HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2602","checkdouble":"194961"},{"date":"10:07 21/08","title":"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \"tr\u1ea3m\" Fabinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-sau-khi-tiep-tuc-tram-fabinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Klopp x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng t\u00e2n binh Fabinho b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Palace v\u00ec l\u00fd do chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi ra h\u01a1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fabinho t\u1eeb Monaco h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Liverpool k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Selhurst Park \u0111\u00eam qua. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Fabinho l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch 18 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Crystal Palace.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3m Fabinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3m Fabinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-sau-khi-tiep-tuc-tram-fabinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fabinho b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra, Klopp chia s\u1ebb: <strong>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y qua tu\u1ea7n kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Fabinho. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Liverpool trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a West Ham, Fabinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Anfield.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i t\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1eady n\u00ean nh\u00ecn chung t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Crystal Palace, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p West Ham. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a Klopp \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-crystal-palace-02-liverpool-172-194948.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lien-tuc-toa-sang-mo-salah-van-bi-thay-che-172-194946.html\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Mo Salah v\u1eabn b\u1ecb th\u1ea7y ch\u00ea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2601","checkdouble":"194962"}]}